X9Y4g_9ydPJWBJwxajayjC5ZcowuWU&h=9f645c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2046720/org/f5a29e632f7d866df421333eb068fb5f.jpg/jsiktlo8F8VMmjphih3aLA6SJq9bJpcFUSEMNVEhDDU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2046720%2Forg%2Ff5a29e632f7d866df421333eb068fb5f.jpg%2Fjsiktlo8F8VMmjphih3aLA6SJq9bJpcFUSEMNVEhDDU&h=527fd098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2046719/org/11c123f7b7cb44d33af439d7220e5ebf.jpg/0seyO8YzwdUmTq0iLfPw304iHA1UpKf-TB95PUwfeT0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2046719%2Forg%2F11c123f7b7cb44d33af439d7220e5ebf.jpg%2F0seyO8YzwdUmTq0iLfPw304iHA1UpKf-TB95PUwfeT0&h=59ad80dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2046718/org/f78b6ce378e33c5272c086088ecd6f8e.jpg/giO9v8Ud6Ggact1MuVKJqOI7WnDJE8O2CMSofAjEqHw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2046718%2Forg%2Ff78b6ce378e33c5272c086088ecd6f8e.jpg%2FgiO9v8Ud6Ggact1MuVKJqOI7WnDJE8O2CMSofAjEqHw&h=bcc7a02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2046716/org/cb7dc8b4c69173301128dbff42e5d42a.jpg/i3yjasq5Nns30rOwPQ5fpH95aBwne6P84FN_POBTfzw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2046716%2Forg%2Fcb7dc8b4c69173301128dbff42e5d42a.jpg%2Fi3yjasq5Nns30rOwPQ5fpH95aBwne6P84FN_POBTfzw&h=b581e122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽到雞排妹有男朋友呢個消息，相信好多人都會唔開心。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹（鄭家純）一向都是男性心中台灣的女神代表，可以說是提起台灣性感女神的話，就自不然想起她。當然，除了與她慣於在台灣節目或出鏡時大派福利有關之外，她其實甚有生意頭腦。繼早前的寫真推出之外，11月份又有由雞排妹帶團兼陪玩、全程充當翻譯的日本賞楓3日2夜團，推出時還在網上引起一陣哄動。<br />\n<br />\n據台灣周刊《時報周刊》報導，「雞排妹」在近日承認了脫離單身一族行列，並表示該男朋友是來自日本的。據報導，這位幸運兒是一名日本小兒科醫生，雞排妹還形容他的外型似韓國男演員孔劉，戀情更是已有半年之久。「雞排妹」接受訪問時稱，雙方認識始於一次年初到日本留學的時候，當時「雞排妹」為體驗當地生活，同時也為直播節目找靈感，但基於當地人不願入鏡的關係，就決定透過手機交友程式找朋友飯聚，因此才與現任男友認識。「雞排妹」接受台灣傳媒訪問時說：「他很喜歡攝影，所以我們會到處玩、到處拍。」<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹（鄭家純）還表示，雙方是「認真在談戀愛」。為了克服遠距離戀愛，她還會每個月飛到日本兩次，而男友也會到台灣找她。<br />\n<br />\n不過睇晒IG相就唔見有佢男朋友嘅踪影，到底呢次係咪另類宣傳手法呢？就真係得佢本人先知。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：林迅景<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/254423/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E9%9B%9E%E6%8E%92%E5%A6%B9%E9%84%AD%E5%AE%B6%E7%B4%94%E5%91%8A%E5%88%A5%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%85%E7%94%B7%E5%BF%83%E7%A2%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F254423%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E9%259B%259E%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25B4%2594%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%2588%25A5%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25AE%2585%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25A2%258E-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%258B%25E9%2580%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2591%25A2%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AD%2598&d=YHOK1jkDVubwOHU1GrJP%2FTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=bc77f293\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/254423/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E9%9B%9E%E6%8E%92%E5%A6%B9%E9%84%AD%E5%AE%B6%E7%B4%94%E5%91%8A%E5%88%A5%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%85%E7%94%B7%E5%BF%83%E7%A2%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%98</a>"},{"pid":"b323072766423cc5e8c5c73553d4ace168a94599","tid":887532,"uid":45268,"like":6,"dislike":77,"score":-71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"佢不嬲唔係單身，佢做左我老婆好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b202bbb4777f7177cfea49e4adee65c6e0eceb5d","tid":887532,"uid":86727,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/2231cc2fcb00071d674d69d0949cb763/5C7CB43E/t51.2885-15/e35/44307571_1200335916786629_402